00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:01,400
[Tang Jiale] Let's watch the match
between Yu Feng and Xing Yao.

27
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:04,240
-That is a good idea.
-[Tang Jiale] Let's go.

28
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:08,120
[Yu Feng students]
Yu Feng, come on! Yu Feng, winner!

29
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:12,080
Yu Feng, come on!

30
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:13,759
[grunts]

31
