It's 6-1. The first doubles, Yu Feng wins.

32
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:18,920
YU FENG HIGH SCHOOL
VS XING YAO HIGH SCHOOL 6-1

33
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:22,520
Xing Yao is the top seed.
How did they lose two matches in a row?

34
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:27,040
Yu Feng is an unknown tennis team.

35
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:31,320
They are not a seed team,
but they earned a place in the top eight.

36
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,120
[scoffs]
It is so surprising.

37
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,240
[snickers]

38
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,480
Yu Feng had a head start.

39
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,440
The situation is favorable to them.

40
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:44,800
And now the cheering squad
of Xing Yao is quiet.

41
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:47,200
You are seriously learning things
even when watching matches.

42
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:49,880
I will write about that
in the next feature story.

43
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,200
Yes.

44
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,160
[soft chuckle]

45
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,480
It is Xu Ziping's turn now.

46
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,280
[bird squawks]

47
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:07,280
I heard that you are the best in Yu Feng.

48
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:09,680
[snickers]
But you are playing so early.

49
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:12,320
Does that mean you have nobody else
on your team?

50
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,280
It doesn't matter.

51
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,320
I will defeat you

52
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:17,760
in 20 minutes.

53
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:19,160
[snickers]

54
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,320
You can try.

55
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:23,120
Where is your captain?

56
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,320
Why isn't he here?

57
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:28,480
He doesn't have to be here
because we are stronger than you.

58
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,680
Then listen to me carefully.
I am Xu Ziping.

59
00:03:31,280 --> 00:03:33,160
You will mention my name when you go back.

60
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:35,240
[snickers]
Pardon?

61
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:37,000
Xu Ziping.
[chuckles]

62
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,600
I've never heard of it before.

63
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:41,640
Prepare an explanation to Ji Jingwu
about why you lost to me.

64
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,880
[scoffs]

65
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:47,960
The main players in Xing Yao

66
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,960
should be different from the others
in their team.

67
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:55,160
You mean the players
in the previous two matches

68
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,520
were not the main players in Xing Yao?

69
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,560
Yes.

70
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:02,280
Oh, is that so?

71
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,840
[Tang Jiale] If they lose the match again,

72
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,600
that would be interesting.

73
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,880
[Ziping grunts]

74
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,240
[coach groans]

75
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,120
-[grunts]
-[man 1] Coach!

76
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:20,079
Principal, we want to form a new team.

77
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:23,040
We want to compete in the National League
on behalf of the school.

78
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,519
I will give you one last chance.

79
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,839
[Yu Feng's principal]
You must win the match,

80
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:31,240
or I will dismiss the team again.

81
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,800
-[thwacks]
-[whooshes]

82
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,040
[grunts]

83
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,760
[umpire 2] It's 1-0,
Yu Feng takes the lead.

84
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,520
[sighs]

85
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:46,080
Hu Liangliang from Xing Yao
didn't have any reaction to the balls.

86
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:48,600
It seems Xing Yao didn't prepare
well enough for the opponents.

87
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,000
Why didn't he compete with us?

88
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:55,520
Because we already won
before he could play.

89
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,960
I didn't expect him to be so great.

90
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:01,560
If Lu Xia had lost in the last match,
he would have played with our captain.

91
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,640
The result would have been unpredictable.

92
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,080
I won't lose.

93
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,680
I was being hypothetical.

94
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:10,600
We wouldn't have let you play
if we had known you hurt your eyes.

95
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:13,320
Then we would have seen the battle
between the two captains.

96
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,560
I won't lose anyway.

97
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,400
[sighs]

98
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:21,840
If Xu Ziping came up first,
the result might have been different.

99
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,640
[Sha] I interviewed him before.

100
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,920
He is very determined to win the match.

101
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,320
He also has great abilities.

102
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,280
I know this person.

103
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:33,240
He used to be the trump card
of No. 5 High School.

104
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:35,360
[Yan Zhiming] They are a strong team
in the division.

105
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,640
You even know about this?

106
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:40,040
Huh? Why didn't you tell us
when we were competing with Yu Feng?

107
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,920
I didn't find out the connection
between these two people

108
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,040
until Qiao Chen mentioned

109
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:48,600
that Xu Ziping transferred
from another place two years ago.

110
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,920
That was when I found out.

111
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:52,120
When did I mention that?

112
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,360
[soft chuckle]

113
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:56,520
Maybe when you were too focused
on his sister.

114
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:58,960
[exhales sharply]

115
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,480
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

116
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,160
[grunts]

117
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,400
[groans, pants]

118
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:10,200
The match is over, the score is 6-0.
Yu Feng wins.

119
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,240
-Great!
-Great!

120
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,800
[sighs]

121
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,080
Sorry.

122
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:25,000
I just needed 15 minutes to defeat you.

123
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:26,880
[breathing heavily]

124
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:31,520
[Yanjiang] Captain, well done!

125
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,640
[somber music]

126
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,360
[gasps]

127
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,880
Hello, Coach.

128
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:47,760
Hu Liangliang lost the game
by 0-6 as a regular.

129
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:50,120
-[exhales sharply]
-[Jingwu] I didn't expect this to happen.

130
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,400
[Xing Yao's coach]
Hu Liangliang is disqualified

131
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,520
-as a regular player from this moment.
-Okay.

132
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:58,200
I will inform Song Ci
to report for duty next week.

133
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,520
[panting]

134
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:04,200
[Xing Yao students] Xing Yao, come on!
Xing Yao!

135
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:06,720
-Xing Yao!
-Xing Yao, come on!

136
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,120
[sighs sharply]

137
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,880
Go. Hmm?

138
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,440
[sighs]

139
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:21,840
[Ze] Go.

140
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,200
[gasps]

141
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,200
Guan Yue.

142
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:26,640
Thank you for your guidance
and help these days.

143
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:29,040
[Yue] Why? What do you mean?

144
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:31,760
-Are you going to retreat from our team?
-No, no, no.

145
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,760
You are the first person
who acknowledged me.

146
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:36,280
[Yu] You didn't do that
because I am a brother of someone.

147
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,600
I really appreciate you.

148
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:40,320
Plus, I don't think aiming
to win is wrong.

149
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:43,640
So I decided to compete
with my own strength in the future.

150
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,560
Is that okay?

151
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,680
Don't let me down.

152
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,640
[Yu] No, I won't.

153
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,040
We will win in the next round.

154
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,160
[exhales sharply]

155
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,720
Good luck, Zhuo Yu.

156
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:06,040
I will do my best,
you don't need to remind me.

157
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:11,440
If we can both
be in the national competition,

158
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:14,120
we can compete together then.

159
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,080
[snickers]

160
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,760
I would rather compete with Siyang.

161
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:17,680
[soft chuckle]

162
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,880
Let's go home for dinner tonight.

163
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,440
No.

164
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:24,120
Your mom is cooking
your favorite roast pork.

165
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,760
[sighs]
I will get some of my things anyway.

166
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,000
It depends.

167
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:30,320
Forget it.
I will call to stop her from cooking.

168
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,960
-You don't like it anyway.
-Stop.

169
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,400
I just said I would go back
and pick some things up.

170
00:08:39,280 --> 00:08:40,720
I am so hungry.

171
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,960
What's taking him so long?

172
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:50,080
Huh? What are you doing here?

173
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,400
We are waiting for Jiale.

174
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,360
He said he will treat us
to a meal if he loses.

175
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,480
Huh? But everybody is gone now.

176
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:59,440
What?

177
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,880
He escaped?

178
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,840
[sighs]

179
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,840
[Yu] Today, when you
were competing... Hmm...

180
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,520
[Zhuo Zhi] Was I handsome?

181
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:12,920
A little bit.

182
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:17,000
Hey! Why are you taking photos of me?

183
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,520
It is so rare to hear you praise me.

184
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,360
I must record it, right?

185
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,960
[Yu groans]

186
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,160
[chuckles]

187
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:30,160
If it wasn't Guan Yue
who taught me Jump Smash,

188
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:33,240
would you still defeat him
with your full strength?

189
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,200
[snickers]

190
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:36,840
I don't have to use my full strength
to defeat him.

191
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,120
[scoffs]

192
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:42,240
It is true.

193
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,320
However,

194
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:47,640
playing in a match with full strength
must be a wonderful experience.

195
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:50,880
Yes, it was great.

196
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,960
No matter who you compete with,

197
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:58,840
even if it's with an invincible genius
and you know you will lose anyway,

198
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:03,160
you still hope the opponent
will do his best to compete with you.

199
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:08,080
So will you take every match seriously
like you did today?

200
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,640
If you are bullied...

201
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:11,960
[sighs]

202
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:13,640
I will.

203
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,440
[light music]

204
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,040
[Yu sighs]

205
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:27,600
[Tang Jiale grunts]

206
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:30,480
I should hit the last ball.

207
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:32,800
In this case, we can react more quickly.

208
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,480
[grunting]

209
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:36,160
It is so annoying.

210
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,080
[exhales sharply]

211
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:46,000
Okay. So much for introspection.

212
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,800
Hmm.

213
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,440
[Dayong] I knew you would be here.

214
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:58,880
Hey, Dachi, I came here alone.

215
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:00,760
[Dayong sighs]

216
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,400
Since we became partners,

217
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:05,040
we always come here for introspection
after losing a game.

218
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:07,000
How many times have we been here?

219
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,800
I can't remember.

220
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:13,360
I don't know how many times
we have lost to the seniors.

221
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,680
[both sigh]

222
00:11:15,760 --> 00:11:19,000
I promise we will never come here again.

223
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:20,880
[sighs]

224
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:23,280
[light music]

225
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,280
[Tang Jiale] Next time,

226
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,160
we will start to sprint.

227
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:31,040
-What about the goal?
-Don't you know?

228
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:35,160
Of course, to win all the matches

229
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,360
and be the champion
of the future national competition.

230
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:44,880
[cat meows]

231
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,040
[meowing continues]

232
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,040
[Baiyang] Meow.

233
00:12:02,560 --> 00:12:04,720
Meow, meow.

234
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,320
Meow.

235
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:09,760
Ahh.

236
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:11,800
I know what you like.

237
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:20,040
-[cat purrs]
-Meow.

238
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,680
Meow.

239
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:25,840
Meow.

240
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:28,520
YU QING

241
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:30,680
[school bell tolling]

242
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,880
[indistinct chatter]

243
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:45,600
Eh? Siyang, you are still here?

244
00:12:45,680 --> 00:12:46,960
Oh. Coach.

245
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:51,280
[exhales sharply]

246
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,560
The last match just ended,

247
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:56,160
and you're already researching
about the next opponent.

248
00:12:56,800 --> 00:12:58,240
[Coach Qi] Luckily, I came back here.

249
00:12:58,320 --> 00:13:02,800
Otherwise, nobody will find out
that our captain is so hardworking.

250
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:05,160
We will gain more confidence
if we start earlier.

251
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:09,560
[inhales sharply]
So you will play in the next match?

252
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:11,640
[somber music]

253
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:13,880
[sighs]

254
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,080
How about your arm?

255
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,440
Please don't worry.

256
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:21,160
I won't force myself
if my arm is not okay.

257
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,320
[sighs deeply]

258
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:26,880
When you realize your arm is not okay,
it will be too late.

259
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:31,680
Each of our team members
has unlimited potential.

260
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,400
However,

261
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,880
they need time to grow up.

262
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,080
[sighs]

263
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:40,720
But I don't know
whether the successor in your mind

