00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:43,800
can grow fast enough to catch up with you.

265
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:45,080
[exhales sharply]

266
00:13:48,680 --> 00:13:49,600
[Peng gasps]

267
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:52,760
This is actually fun to play with.

268
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:55,360
These are bouncy balls.

269
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:57,440
They are suitable for beginners like us.

270
00:13:57,520 --> 00:13:59,200
We can practice playing tennis on our own.

271
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:01,400
Then we can use it to practice tennis
in the future.

272
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,800
[soft chuckle]

273
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:11,240
This is the first time
we bought tennis balls ourselves.

274
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:14,760
Should we draw something on the ball
as a mark?

275
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:18,640
Then let's draw Lu Xia.

276
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,200
[chuckles]
Okay.

277
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,440
[light music]

278
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:27,680
[chuckling]

279
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:35,480
Look.

280
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,040
[Peng] This is my drawing.

281
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,200
Hmm...

282
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:42,120
Hmm?

283
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:43,880
Hm!

284
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:47,640
[gasps]
How did you do this?

285
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:49,240
Help me draw one, please.

286
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:52,080
-Then you can have mine.
-Mm-hmm.

287
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:54,080
[chuckles]

288
00:15:05,040 --> 00:15:06,960
[phone ringing]

289
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:13,840
[Lu Xia] I am on my way.
Don't call me anymore.

290
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:15,720
[Xiangqian] I know
you don't have many clothes.

291
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:17,520
So I want to buy some for you.

292
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:20,360
-But look at how you treat me.
-If there's nothing else, I will hang up.

293
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:23,320
[Xiangqian] Uh, if you get there early,
don't pick clothes by yourself.

294
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:25,480
If you get clothes
like the ones you have at home,

295
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:26,480
I won't pay for them.

296
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:28,880
Then you can buy some
and bring them back to me.

297
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:31,040
The Chinese saying goes,

298
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:34,080
"Better teach a man to fish
than to give him a fish".

299
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:36,800
[sighs]
Okay, I know.

300
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:39,480
[Xiangqian] Don't wear the team uniform.

301
00:15:40,880 --> 00:15:42,880
[light music]

302
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,600
[Xiuwen] ...nor has a nice figure,

303
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:57,160
hm, nor has a dress sense...

304
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,480
[chief editor laughing]

305
00:15:58,560 --> 00:16:00,560
[Xiuwen] She's also pretty careless

306
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:02,120
and ill-tempered.

307
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,480
[all laughing]

308
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:06,960
My question is,

309
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:10,760
who taught you to use GoPro
to record the tennis match?

310
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:13,480
[chief editor] You even deleted the photos
from the camera.

311
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,560
Eh?

312
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:16,560
Now, there is something surprising
as well.

313
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:18,240
-[chief editor laughs]
-[sighs]

314
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:21,400
Sir, please don't make fun of me.

315
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,560
It is so embarrassing.

316
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,240
But...

317
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:27,280
there hasn't been anyone

318
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:30,640
who recorded a sports match
like a documentary.

319
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:31,920
This kind of method...

320
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:33,760
is new in our field.

321
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,520
[chief editor]
Hey, maybe after we broadcast this,

322
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,920
the senior high tennis league
we are focusing on

323
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,600
will become more famous.

324
00:16:42,040 --> 00:16:42,960
Okay.

325
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:46,600
[all giggling]

326
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:51,680
[Sha] I am totally ruined by those boys.

327
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:55,680
I am a professional.
I won't be looked down on.

328
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:56,800
[inhales sharply]

329
00:16:56,880 --> 00:17:00,360
[Sha] I am a professional.
I am a professional. I am a professional.

330
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:02,360
[beeping]

331
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:04,200
[Peng] Hmm?

332
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,119
-[machine beeping]
-[gasping]

333
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:08,920
[sighs]

334
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,000
[sighs sharply]

335
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:16,560
[phone ringing]

336
00:17:18,119 --> 00:17:19,200
[gasps]
Ying.

337
00:17:19,280 --> 00:17:21,720
-[Ying] Hm?
-The vending machine is broken.

338
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:24,720
I'll go to the store to buy some drinks.
Go ahead and practice first.

339
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:26,599
[Ying] Okay. Be careful.

340
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:27,680
Come back soon.

341
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,240
Okay. See you later.

342
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:31,560
[phone beeps]

343
00:17:32,560 --> 00:17:33,480
[exhales sharply]

344
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:41,360
[comical music]

345
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:52,440
Oh!

346
00:17:52,920 --> 00:17:54,240
This is the flavor I like.

347
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:55,360
I am so lucky.

348
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:57,440
SHEN QIANSHI
CAPTAIN OF NO. 3 HIGH SCHOOL TENNIS TEAM

349
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:03,200
[comical music]

350
00:18:09,640 --> 00:18:10,520
[woman 1 grunts]

351
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:16,000
[woman 2] One more ball.

352
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:19,920
[Ying grunts]

353
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:21,880
[sighs]

354
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:25,600
[thwacks]

355
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:33,240
I'm surprised
that you're passionate about tennis.

356
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,400
[gasps]

357
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:39,200
[romantic music]

358
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:40,920
Thank you.

359
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:45,360
[soft chuckle]
Why are you here?

360
00:18:46,680 --> 00:18:48,960
I think this is fun.
Let me play for a while, okay?

361
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:55,200
[thwacking]

362
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,120
[grunts]

363
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:12,480
Huh?

364
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:18,080
[thwacking]

365
00:19:22,320 --> 00:19:24,640
It turns out
that there is another way of playing it.

366
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,200
[grunts]

367
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:33,200
[Ying sighs]

368
00:19:34,520 --> 00:19:35,600
[snickers]

369
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:37,440
Are you from Yu Qing Tennis Club?

370
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,000
You are not tall.

371
00:19:40,600 --> 00:19:43,400
Are you from Grade 10?
You have good tennis skills.

372
00:19:46,760 --> 00:19:47,680
[Qianshi] It's a pity.

373
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:49,960
If you can put your center of gravity
on the pivot foot,

374
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:51,720
you will have more explosive power.

375
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:52,840
Thank you.

376
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:02,960
-[thwacks]
-[whooshes]

377
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:06,640
[upbeat music]

378
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:12,160
[Qianshi] He is actually left-handed.

379
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:17,840
The ball hit by his left hand
has a totally different power.

380
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,240
I'll be late for my class.

381
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:22,520
NO. 3 HIGH SCHOOL

382
00:20:24,440 --> 00:20:26,040
Sorry, I broke it.

383
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:28,080
Never mind.

384
00:20:28,360 --> 00:20:30,560
I can tie it myself.

385
00:20:31,360 --> 00:20:34,280
That person seems
to be from No. 3 High School.

386
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,560
So be it.

387
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:40,200
I'll give you a new one as compensation.
I have something to deal with. See you.

388
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:47,160
[camera shutter clicks]

389
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:52,960
[playful music]

390
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,200
Whoa.

391
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:57,960
It was her again.

392
00:20:58,920 --> 00:21:02,000
If you want to teach her how to play,
then you should be serious about it.

393
00:21:05,480 --> 00:21:06,560
[gasps]

394
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:09,840
-Ying.
-Oh?

395
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:11,520
Was that Lu Xia?

396
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:13,480
Yes.

397
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:15,720
He just taught me how to play tennis.

398
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:19,000
I wouldn't go and buy drinks if I knew.

399
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:24,120
It seems you still need
my help with girls.

400
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:33,240
[beeps]

401
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:35,400
[sighs]

402
00:21:39,080 --> 00:21:41,080
[playful music]

403
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:43,080
[Zhuo Zhi] Zhuo Yu. Are you okay?

404
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,200
[gasps]

405
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:59,280
[soft chuckle]

406
00:22:04,280 --> 00:22:05,240
[Zhou Zhi gasps]

407
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:07,120
What a coincidence.

408
00:22:08,080 --> 00:22:10,960
It's surprising that Lu Xia dresses
like this in his daily life.

409
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:12,720
It looks really good.

410
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:18,360
Hey, your brother looks good in those.

411
00:22:18,800 --> 00:22:19,680
Mm-hmm.

412
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:21,640
He looks good in any clothes.

413
00:22:27,040 --> 00:22:27,880
[Zhuo Zhi] Hmm?

414
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:31,040
Is it necessary
to hurt each other like this?

415
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,040
I am just telling the truth.

416
00:22:34,040 --> 00:22:35,760
[chuckling]

417
00:22:39,320 --> 00:22:41,120
You have a good relationship
with your brother.

418
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:43,040
-[staff] This is our new design...
-No, I don't.

419
00:22:43,120 --> 00:22:44,080
-This one...
-[Yu] I...

420
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,240
I am forced to be here.

421
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:46,800
[Zhuo Zhi] Let me have a look at this.

422
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:49,320
Nevertheless, it is a surprise...

423
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:51,360
that you are here.

424
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:52,520
I am also forced to be here.

425
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:54,600
[comical music]

426
00:23:05,360 --> 00:23:07,360
[comical music continues]

427
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:14,360
If we can qualify,

428
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:17,880
I hope to compete with you
in the national competition.

429
00:23:18,080 --> 00:23:20,040
Isn't your brother
the only one you want to defeat?

430
00:23:20,120 --> 00:23:22,640
[scoffs]
My brother has always been my goal.

431
00:23:23,120 --> 00:23:25,440
-Is there any other color...
-[Yu] But since I lost to you,

432
00:23:25,520 --> 00:23:26,800
-[Yu] I realized something.
-What?

433
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,840
-[Zhou Zhi] Just the largest size?
-Aside from him,

434
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:31,000
I have many strong competitors
to compete with.

435
00:23:31,560 --> 00:23:32,840
[Yu] So I will become stronger.

436
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:34,920
Next time, when we meet in the court,

437
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:37,840
I will not lose to you.

438
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:39,240
Me too.

439
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:40,920
I will be stronger.

440
00:23:41,600 --> 00:23:42,960
[Lu Xia] I will not lose to anyone.

441
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:44,560
[gasps]

442
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:46,560
[exhales sharply]

443
00:23:50,720 --> 00:23:52,880
I saw you chatting happily
with your friends.

444
00:23:53,160 --> 00:23:54,880
Why don't you have anything to say to me?

445
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:05,080
The crispy part is the most delicious.

446
00:24:09,800 --> 00:24:10,760
[soft chuckle]

447
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:17,040
[Ayumi Yoshida]
Why did we stop on the bridge?

448
00:24:17,120 --> 00:24:18,400
We are just slowing down.

449
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:21,080
[Mitsuhiko Tsiburaya]
Because it will be Asakusa Station

450
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,600
after we cross the bridge.

451
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:24,320
For the summer vacation homework...

452
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:25,600
-[sighs]
-[phone dings]

453
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:28,200
...let's make a model
for the Todo Suzuki Tower

454
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:31,080
and its surroundings. How is that?

455
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,280
[Genta Kojima]
Wow, that will be amazing.

456
00:24:32,360 --> 00:24:33,760
Aren't you expecting this series?

457
00:24:33,840 --> 00:24:35,400
-You'll miss it if you don't watch.
-[Ayumi Yoshida] Conan, Ai.

458
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:37,080
Let's make it together.

459
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:39,440
It's okay. I know who the murderer is.

460
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:40,920
[indistinct on TV]

461
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,160
Have you seen it at school?

462
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:43,840
My friend just told me.

463
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:45,440
He has seen it abroad.

464
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:47,720
[soft chuckle]

465
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,440
[Ayumi Yoshida] Let's take more pictures.

466
00:24:49,520 --> 00:24:52,680
So you have been texting
a friend living abroad, right?

467
00:24:53,280 --> 00:24:54,200
Mm-hm.

468
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:55,880
Hmm.

469
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:59,120
Great, you have a friend abroad.

470
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:03,080
[Yu] You can click on the hyperlink.

471
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:04,800
There are videos from around the world.

472
00:25:04,880 --> 00:25:06,920
[Lu Xia] Okay, I will check now.

473
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:08,960
Enjoy your TV.

474
00:25:13,360 --> 00:25:16,680
Welcome to attend
the doubles match of our club.

475
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:17,760
Lu Xia.

476
00:25:18,320 --> 00:25:19,640
-[inhales sharply]
-Huh?

477
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:21,120
Oh.
[chuckles]

478
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:22,800
-[knocking]
-[sighs]

479
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:23,960
What are you doing tomorrow?

480
00:25:24,600 --> 00:25:25,840
Practice.

481
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:28,000
Then you have nothing to do.
I'll wake you up tomorrow.

482
00:25:28,080 --> 00:25:29,080
Okay.

483
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,360
[gasps]
Huh?

484
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:32,960
Go to bed early.
You need enough sleep to get taller.

485
00:25:34,840 --> 00:25:37,240
[sighing]

486
00:25:38,840 --> 00:25:40,320
[indistinct chatter]

487
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:44,760
♪ If you don’t like to listen to my songs
Please cover your ears ♪

488
00:25:44,840 --> 00:25:48,160
♪ Next I’m going to kick off
And breakthrough your eardrums ♪

489
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:51,440
♪ Until it reaches the depths of your soul
So that you will idolize me ♪

490
00:25:51,520 --> 00:25:52,480
♪ Follow me... ♪

491
00:25:55,120 --> 00:25:56,200
Where are you taking me?

492
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,720
[playful music]

493
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:01,800
You must be hungry, right?

494
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:05,480
Eat.

495
00:26:14,040 --> 00:26:15,880
I remember something.

496
00:26:16,160 --> 00:26:19,760
My friend's niece
wants to learn how to play tennis.

497
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:21,400
What does it have to do with me?

498
00:26:21,760 --> 00:26:24,160
I thought you could teach her.

499
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,960
I am not going. You can go if you want.

500
00:26:27,240 --> 00:26:28,600
Oh, okay.

501
00:26:28,680 --> 00:26:31,720
When you meet her, remember to be serious.
Don't be casual.

502
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:33,640
You can go yourself.

503
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:38,160
The baizi is made by my friend.

504
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:40,880
You already ate one.

505
00:26:41,320 --> 00:26:44,560
Just do it to repay
my love and care. Okay?

506
00:26:47,360 --> 00:26:48,200
Oh.

507
00:26:48,560 --> 00:26:50,640
What a coincidence. It's here. Look.
[chuckles]

508
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:52,000
We're here.

509
00:26:54,280 --> 00:26:55,440
[sighs sharply]

510
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:01,360
-[Ying] Hey.
-[Peng chuckles]

511
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:02,440
[Ying] Lu Xia is coming.

512
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:05,760
Lu Xia.

513
00:27:06,320 --> 00:27:07,480
[Peng] You are finally here.

514
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:14,200
You're the niece of my father's friend?

515
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:18,800
My auntie said your father thought
we were passionate about playing tennis,

516
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:20,600
so he wanted to guide us.

517
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:22,840
We knew you would be here.

518
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:27,680
Where is your father?

519
00:27:28,360 --> 00:27:30,240
He has already left. Do you want to learn?

520
00:27:30,320 --> 00:27:31,320
[both] Mm-hm.

521
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:34,120
[playful music]

522
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:36,840
-[thwacking]
-[groans]

523
00:27:38,120 --> 00:27:39,200
[Peng sighs sharply]

524
00:27:50,320 --> 00:27:51,200
[grunts]

525
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,880
[Ying groans]

526
00:27:56,840 --> 00:27:58,000
[sighs sharply]

527
00:27:59,080 --> 00:28:00,520
You use too much strength.

528
00:28:01,000 --> 00:28:04,160
Sorry for bothering you to teach us.

529
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,080
Mm-hm.

530
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:07,280
You should lower your knees.

