683
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:37,280
put their body in a natural way.

684
00:36:38,520 --> 00:36:40,360
-Ah...
-Right.

685
00:36:40,600 --> 00:36:43,200
-You really understand art.
-I do.

686
00:36:44,040 --> 00:36:45,120
[Huang Jing clears throat]

687
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,440
Hey, what about this?

688
00:36:47,520 --> 00:36:48,440
This one...

689
00:36:49,680 --> 00:36:53,040
