690
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:55,320
Glasses?

691
00:36:57,680 --> 00:36:58,520
[Huang Jing] Yes.

692
00:36:59,080 --> 00:37:00,040
Look at the glasses.

693
00:37:01,920 --> 00:37:03,440
Just like playing tennis,

694
00:37:04,200 --> 00:37:06,880
